name: Kiss Socks.
description:
Forever Ashbury. Brand Socks Features: $18

High performance moisture management fabric for comfort and moisture-control
Seamless toe for added comfort
Fabric: 96% polyester/3% spandex/1% rubber
Machine wash cold & tumble dry

Nike Elite Socks Features: $32

Dri-FIT fabric to wick sweat away and help keep your feet dry and comfortable
Rib cuffs for a snug fit
Footstrike cushioning for comfort
Arch support for stability and a secure fit
Left/right specific for enhanced fit
Fabric: 62% polyester/21% nylon/15% cotton/2% spandex
Machine wash cold & tumble dry
*We use the highest quality patented ink technology to print our socks that produce premium full-color, photographic-quality images that bonds into the fabric and will not crack, peel, fade or wash away. Our socks are pre stretched so that when worn, you get the highest resolution graphic without distortion and is incomparable to our competitors. Your socks may feel compressed when you receive them, but after a few washes/wears, the cushioning will expand back. Wrinkles or spots may or may not occur at the bottom of the sock, which are not seen when worn.

**For socks, due to hygienic reasons we cannot accept Refunds or Exchanges. No Exceptions.

***We only use 100% AUTHENTIC Nike Elite Socks with Original Packaging, No Variants or Defects. We are not a Nike store nor are we affiliated with Nike, Inc. Nike Swoosh and Nike name are registered trademarks of Nike, Inc.

name: XL Drip Kiss Vinyl Decal.
description:
If you follow our Instagr.am, Twitter, and FaceBook, chances are that you've seen our Drip Kiss sticker sliding off of the window onto the paint on some of the cars we post. We consider ourselves a LifeStyle brand and because of that, we live it. We encapsulate all of our interests and channel it into a creative outlet we call Forever Ashbury. With motor sports being one of our main passions, we thought of a creative and unique way to rep it on our cars and motorcycles but not limited to everything else you can sticker up! EVERY CAR NEEDS ONE!

These 11 inch wide by 14 inch tall stickers are available in Purple, Teal, Brushed Aluminum, Pink & White for $11.99 with free shipping to all 50 states.
